Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了個噁心的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 我把人柱帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人？突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩維
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩維？這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎧甲的阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（好痛痛痛 阿爾 鎧甲的角戳到了）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真讓人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然從肚子裡跑出人來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩…海姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼的手和腳 鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛力克兄弟嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是和誰弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是指馮·霍恩海姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們和他是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真驚人 那傢伙居然生了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你們的姓不是愛力克嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克是母親的姓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 倒是你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼和霍恩海姆長得一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}（他不可能會死）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}（但是居然生了小孩）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 這個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位沒了左手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨折了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治 治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的是肋骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是重要的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好保護自己的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙沒有做任何動作就發動了鍊金術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且沒有把裝甲弄薄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 不是等價交換
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那裡面是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話就還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等 他是我的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在我這個人柱的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就放他一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說是不需要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙被人造人稱為父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是製造了他們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然治好了我們的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真看不慣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個態度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在嘲笑人類是蠢貨一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會認為地上爬的蟲子是蠢貨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使蟲子再掙扎 等級相差太多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼感覺都不會有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來 你們人類也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你給我們治好了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但果然沒法共存
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來諸惡的根源是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣分出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候雜魚就先放一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說我們是雜魚 小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不點？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下首領
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那傢伙不做任何動作就能鍊成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法發動…鍊金術？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德 阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個鬍鬚男做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼無法使用鍊金術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些下等生物真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得了強大的力量就自我驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道那是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們以為現在的繁榮都是靠自己的力量形成的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真滑稽 這些愚蠢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說了若能回來就全都告訴我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不記得和你們這些蟲子做過什麼約定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得太多了 恩維
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為素材倒是不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能增加可用的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓賢者之石流進去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利的話 就能製造出以人類為基礎的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 大部分的人會因為承受不了石頭的力量而死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你們幹這種事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我們 恩維
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼無法發動鍊金術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 鬍鬚男
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子還有人在等他回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話 就無法開槍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 別開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了尋找賢者之石而來到這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在他們專程給我石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就如你所願 給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我說了…不准出手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣待著別動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要成為清國皇帝的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼小鬼會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的身體交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給本大人使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 這個身體就給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了接受你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說不會拒絕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要成為清國皇帝的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有能接受二三十個人的廣大胸懷怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡豪爽的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是別後悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果空手回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒臉去見為我斷臂的臣下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了到手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要絕對性的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原來就知道很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那強欲 我很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你的覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說這個身體的主人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個容器被我古利德大人拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是麟…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那個古利德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在達普利斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說那是哪個古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說你前任的古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們所知道的古利德是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個挺有意思的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙爽快地接受了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼會這麼容易讓你佔據身體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 麟 麟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人好討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是人 卻又不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 這裡的人都不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅 太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道怎麼回事 感動的再會？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來和人造人不是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華大人在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有看到呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說就是那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小個子的就是鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然玩弄少女的純情 你這個飯粒男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 妳這飯粒女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哥哥 你對這孩子做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}什麼也沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是沒吃到的伊修瓦爾人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不順從的人民嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說作為破壞之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我們添了不少麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去收拾掉 庫拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在無法使用鍊金術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踐踏了少女之心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還誘拐了小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天誅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是無法發動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能在這裡使用術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼斯卡和那孩子能？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 雖然不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是打破目前這個狀況的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來告訴你伊修瓦爾內亂的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為內亂導火索的射殺兒童事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個叫恩維的傢伙變成軍隊將校幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部是那些傢伙設計好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來得讓我好好來問問你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要毀滅我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據你的回答 我要把你們送到神的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你們沒資格去我等伊修瓦爾同胞沉睡之神的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不會得到安息和救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為人類幹得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德 把外部人員排除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不相信 麟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個確實是姚家的麟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟軟的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你為什麼能用鍊金術？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人體破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是分解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再遲一點的話 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有說過要你救…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們對對自己沒有利益的人毫不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有逃走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡 你能帶著這孩子逃到地面上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要放我跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那個醫生的孩子來說是仇人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 真想揍你一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我非常不願意拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在讓這孩子逃走才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎對他們來說 我們兄弟是貴重的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使留在這裡也不會被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:20:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我要保護著這個女孩突破這裡是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我根本就沒有逃到地面上的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水的分解？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 要幹的話事先說一聲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氫氣加引火 真是幹得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉多尼 用氣味追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有再生力了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不錯的踢腿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我想像中的更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:20:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把麟的身體還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝模作樣 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的國家和蘭芳要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 我抓住他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶到上面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 盡做多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們乖乖待著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不會出手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟就在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再生能力用完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.48,0:23:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把你重新做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶也留下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混沌的人類喲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.17,0:24:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦著 掙扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是活著的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後掙扎之後在我面前跪下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.08,0:24:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.92,0:24:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第29話 愚者的掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.40,0:24:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折斷手腳的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.41,0:24:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能夠再次站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:12.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因為我由於不決
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}輕微的顫抖著  control過了還在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:20.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}太陽也好  運氣（月亮）也罷  完全與我無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:21.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}「只有硬上了吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我這樣勸說自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:30.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情況很糟糕  臨陣逃脫又沒毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}雖然前途未卜  也只能靠膽量獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:37.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}壓制著衝動  尋找敵我之間的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:40.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是勝利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:43.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}能嘗下勝利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:47.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}或者喝下滿腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:51.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二擇其一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操縱命運的輪盤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:00.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}絕好的黃金時間  親自把握機會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}擺出一副撲克臉  設下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:09.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敵人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:16.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}無盡的pressure game  跨越過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:20.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}為了跨越榮耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:24.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代價？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:29.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底捨不得放棄哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:06.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一輪又一輪後依然想在此相見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:13.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}為了不再走散而緊緊牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:16.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}談話直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:18.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}牽手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:24.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就這樣明天後天也一直這樣形影不離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:28.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看著街上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.72,0:22:34.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一個人是無法找到溫暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.07,0:22:39.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道愛原來可以如此堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.74,0:22:45.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在與你相遇之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.39,0:22:50.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一輪又一輪後依然想在此相見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:55.97,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為了不再走散而緊緊牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:01.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為一個人無法入睡  也無法做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:06.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在不安無法到達的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.93,0:23:12.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是沒有星星的夜晚也要繼續將其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:14.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的話能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:17.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}一個人無法走過的道路  如果是兩個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.69,0:23:20.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼著歌走過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.73,0:23:24.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福


